query:
SELECT s.id, s.status, s.scheduledAt, st.name as student_name, wl.id as workout_log_id
FROM sessions s
JOIN students st ON st.id = s.studentId
LEFT JOIN workout_logs wl ON wl.sessionId = s.id
ORDER BY s.scheduledAt DESC
LIMIT 10;
